        dl
          dt Combat aircraft
          dd Military transport aircraft Xian Y-7 and Shaanxi Y-8, Hangars likely to host J-10 and/or J-11 and H-6 bombers!{ref(8)}

          dt Berthing
          dd Yes!{ref(9)}

          dt Over the horizon awareness/targeting!{ref(1)}
          dd Radomes!{ref(10)}, High frequency array radar facility!{ref(11)}, “Elephant cage” direction-finding radar!{ref(13)}, Observation towers, X-band over the horizon radars

          dt Long range missiles
          dd HQ-9B surface-to-air missiles!{ref(14)}, YJ-12B anti-ship cruise missiles, Potential deployment of ground launch cruise missiles!{ref(15)}

