      aside.box.box-hainan
        button.hide &times;
        h2.box-title Hainan Island

        dl
          dt Combat aircraft
          dd JH-7A, J-11B, J-11BH, J-11!{ref(16)}, H&#8209;6
  
          dt Berthing
          dd Yes, Jin-class submarine!{ref(17)}, Shang-class Type 093 nuclear attack submarine!{ref(18)}

          dt Over the horizon awareness/targeting!{ref(1)}
          dd High frequency radars (300km), Low frequency radars (50km), Shaanxi KJ-200 airborne early warning!{ref(19)}, Long range Harbin BZK-005 drones, Guizhou Soar Dragon “Xiang Long” WZ-7 unmanned aerial vehicle!{ref(20)}

          dt Long range missiles
          dd HQ-9 surface-to-air missiles!{ref(21)}, Possibly D-21D and/or DF-26 anti-ship ballistic missiles!{ref(22)}

          dt Short range missiles
